data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION! This 2/2 condo overlooks Terry Cove and has a view second to none in Orange Beach from the 5th Floor. Must SEE! This beautiful complex recently completed a major renovation (Spring 2023) with new windows, sliding doors, railings, exterior paint, and pool resurfacing. The resort style pool and green space also make this a unique and special property. This unit has been beautifully updated and is turn key! Freshly painted, LVP flooring, stainless steel appliances, new HVAC, plus a built in bar and spacious balcony for relaxing. Sold furnished. Marina slips are licensed to the owners for a reasonable yearly fee. Bring your boat, golf cart, kayak or bike and become part of the sought after Bay Back community. Upper lot is for boat trailer parking and golf cart charging station on property as well. The property will be gated and fully fenced again soon. Current assessment due to be paid in full by seller upon closing.
